metadata.name: Florabundance_1_Rose
metadata.description: Meet the Florabundance sisters. Florabundance is a 6 piece 1/1 art collection celebrating floral beauty with a vintage twist. Created using digital collage techniques, mixed with an abstract art signature throughout the collection, each sister is truly unique. She can stand alone proudly or create a breathtakingly beautiful combination when placed next to her equally stunning sisters.
